---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
const pageTitle = "Portfolio";
---
<Layout pageTitle={pageTitle}>
    <div class="gif">
        <img width="300" height="259" alt="TechGif" src="/techgif.webp"/>
    </div>
    <h1>Welcome</h1>
    <small>Quinten Epting (Developer)</small>
    <h2>About</h2>
    <p>
        I'm Quinten Epting, a seasoned technologist with a passion for solving complex problems 
        through innovative technology solutions. With a rich background in cybersecurity, law enforcement, 
        and military operations, I leverage my diverse experiences to bring a unique perspective to software engineering. 
        My expertise spans full-stack development, cloud technologies, and compliance standards, making me a dynamic asset 
        in any tech environment. As a continuous learner, I'm always eager to tackle new challenges and am committed to delivering 
        outstanding results.
    </p>
    <div class="button">
        <a href="/projects/">
            <button class="button">My Projects</button>
        </a>
    </div>
    <h2>Skills</h2>
    <div class="link-images">
        <img width="46" height="46" alt="Python" src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/devicons/devicon/icons/python/python-original.svg"/>
        <img width="46" height="46" alt="Streamlit" src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/devicons/devicon/icons/streamlit/streamlit-original.svg"/>
        <img width="46" height="46" alt="MongoDB" src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/devicons/devicon/icons/mongodb/mongodb-original.svg"/>
        <img width="46" height="46" alt="React" src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/devicons/devicon/icons/react/react-original.svg"/>
        <img width="46" height="46" alt="Netlify" src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/devicons/devicon/icons/netlify/netlify-original.svg" />
        <img width="46" height="46" alt="CSS" src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/devicons/devicon/icons/css3/css3-plain.svg"/>
        <img width="46" height="46" alt="HTML" src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/devicons/devicon/icons/html5/html5-plain.svg"/>
        <img width="46" height="46" alt="JavaScript" src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/devicons/devicon/icons/javascript/javascript-plain.svg"/>
        <img width="46" height="46" alt="git" src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/devicons/devicon/icons/git/git-original.svg"/>
    </div>
    <h2>Interests</h2>
    <p>
        Beyond my professional life, I'm deeply fascinated by all areas of technology, from automation and development to cybersecurity. My enthusiasm doesn't stop there; 
        I'm a big fan of Star Wars and Power Rangers, blending my love for epic narratives with my tech interests. Outside the digital world, I enjoy coaching my son's T-ball team, 
        an experience that enriches my life with community spirit and teamwork. These diverse interests reflect my belief in the importance of balanceâ€”embracing both high-tech pursuits 
        and the simple joys of family time and fandom.
    </p>
</Layout>
<style>
    /* small */
    small {
        display: grid;
        place-items: center;
        background-color: #584966;
        color: #fdebf3;
        border-radius: 6px;
        font-family: 'Josefin Sans', sans-serif;
        font-weight: 600;
        padding: 0.3em 0.6em 0.2em;
    }

    /* Button */
    button {
        background: rgba(0,0,0,0);
        border: 2px solid #78c2ad;
        border-radius: 8px;
        color: #999597;
        font: 600 16px 'Josefin Sans', sans-serif;
        padding: 8px 16px;
        transition: background-color 0.4s, color 0.4s;
    }

    button:hover {
        background-color: #78c2ad;
        color: #1e1e2e;
        cursor: pointer;
    }

    .button {
        text-align: center;
    }

    /* Skill images */
    .link-images img {
        margin: 16px 4px;
    }

    @media only screen and (max-width: 600px) {
        .link-images img {
            height: 30px;
            width: 30px;
            margin: 16px 1px;
        }
    }
</style>
